com.troystopera.jkode - package com.troystopera.jkode
Base package for jKode project containing base implementations for all Executables.
com.troystopera.jkode.components - package com.troystopera.jkode.components
Implementations of the class Component; these classes represent basic compound blocks of code and may return class CtrlStmt.
com.troystopera.jkode.control - package com.troystopera.jkode.control
Classes used to interrupt execution of code.
com.troystopera.jkode.evaluations - package com.troystopera.jkode.evaluations
Implementations of the class Evaluation; these classes return a value during execution of code.
com.troystopera.jkode.exceptions - package com.troystopera.jkode.exceptions
Contains exceptions that may be "thrown" during virtual execution of code.
com.troystopera.jkode.exceptions.compile - package com.troystopera.jkode.exceptions.compile
Implementations of the exception JKodeCompileException; exceptions that would normally be thrown at compile time.
com.troystopera.jkode.exceptions.runtime - package com.troystopera.jkode.exceptions.runtime
Implementations of the exception JKodeRuntimeException; exceptions that would normally be thrown at runtime.
com.troystopera.jkode.exec - package com.troystopera.jkode.exec
Contains classes relating to the virtual runtime/execution of code.
com.troystopera.jkode.exec.override - package com.troystopera.jkode.exec.override
Contains classes used for overriding virtual execution at runtime.
com.troystopera.jkode.format - package com.troystopera.jkode.format
Contains classes for the formatting of virtual code into a human readable String.
com.troystopera.jkode.statements - package com.troystopera.jkode.statements
Implementations of the class Statement; these classes alter values at virtual runtime, but return nothing.
com.troystopera.jkode.vars - package com.troystopera.jkode.vars
Contains classes used in the representation of virtual variables.
